room_title: Escape room "Sweet Dreams" by Escaped In Time in Colorado Springs
room_description: KC is your average, fun loving, 5 year old girl. She loves kittens, puppies, ponies, dolls, coloring, and playing with her toys.  She has quite the active imagination. Her imagination is also vivid in her dreams that sometimes they change the way she views the world.  Your goal is to help restore KC's room to a warm, loving environment so she wakes up in a cozy, loving room.
